snippet.title: Hannah and the Pirate Caves - The Pit (Unused Level)
snippet.description: The Pit is an unused level found within Hannah and the Pirate caves (under the filename 00082a75.fff) and is quite sadistic. I suspected this was one of the featured caves in the Cave of the Week, because the life+gem trap feels *super* familiar to me. Alas, The Pit hasn't a single listing in the Cave Spotlight archives. Check it out yourself: http://www.neopets.com/piratespotlight.phtml
